The paper deals with functional dependencies in the context of incomplete information, which is a common problem in database management systems. Therefore, cs.DB (Databases) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses lattice theory and multi-valued logic, which are topics covered in cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves reasoning and problem-solving, which are topics covered in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
